column2: SELECT m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, m.name as redshift, n.objID, n.distance, p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMagErr_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMagErr_i, p.psfMag_z, p.psfMagErr_z, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMagErr_r, p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMagErr_i, p.fiberMag_i , p.fiberMagErr_i, p.deVRad_i , p.deVRadErr_i, dered_g, p.dered_r, dered_i, dered_z, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z into HSC_CrossMatch_CMASSrng FROM MyDB.HSC_sql_query_CMASSrng_ra_dec AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objID = p.objID
